{"title":"热血颂——援越抗美诗三首","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——援越抗美诗三首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对帝国主义的回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在天空上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在海洋上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在竹刀上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在椰林上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在机枪上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把诗写在椅子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越一把椅子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐着一位老大娘。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘坐在椅子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"椅子下有机关枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老大娘神态端详，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她对南越战士说——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子等敌人到齐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐了你们就开枪……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘一声令下“打”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光遍照南方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越英雄的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在那把椅子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能忘记雷鸣时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵红霞升天上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能忘记风暴里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光射到窗子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿天下革命儿郎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朗诵革命的诗章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都看在这把椅子上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在椅子上的老大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她对全世界这样讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对帝国主义的回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能是这样————"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反抗！战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——战斗！反抗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剥下豺狼的画皮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑看纸老虎的下场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕老大娘的英勇事迹，载《南方来信》第二集。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懦夫与好汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是懦夫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是好汉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懦夫睁眼瞎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好汉身似箭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋下手中雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔出手榴弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸虎长核牙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也得碎两半。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是真理？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是侵略？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用威尔逊说教，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界看得明白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉劝美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快放下屠刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迫击炮对准你了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不怕岘港大火烧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是泥土？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是钢铁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胆小鬼滚开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命者前来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看南越朔二姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单身跨火海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪林弹雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺下敌人的头来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向北望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱一支枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在船头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷报信一封，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捎去给北方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方是骨肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方是心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁敢用利刃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将它分割在两旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在船头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬眼向北望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不能呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割断这条江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾一叶扁舟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载千斤心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相逢在战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸满一江恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举五尺枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里不降帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪里不停桨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捧一江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跪吻大江上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听祖国炮声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起翻天大浪。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}